{"tid":467131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真(求物理神人) 汽水與水 有糖?無糖?神奇!飲料丟水中可分辨","createTime":"2017-11-13T08:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T12:26:57.000Z","uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9980d2a92461b43674641e765f771e23533b3b","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"原LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ttv.com.tw/drama12/NewsScience/view.asp?id=212631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ttv.com.tw%2Fdrama12%2FNewsScience%2Fview.asp%3Fid%3D212631&d=%2FYMK0%2FgWmQ5%2F85T3GOZOdS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=04165004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ttv.com.tw/drama12/NewsScience/view.asp?id=212631</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>但正常方法去試應該係可以成功<br />\n</strong><br />\n但剛剛拍片時需要再做呢一次實驗..<span style=\"color: red;\">.完全唔得!失敗左!!</span><br />\n<br />\n好想知道係咪有D咩原因會令到呢個實驗失敗<br />\n<br />\n1.試左用唔同水<br />\n<br />\n2.轉左新既汽水<br />\n<br />\n3.唔同的器重<br />\n<br />\n最後都係失敗<br />\n<br />\n求物理神人解答到底係咩原因令到個實驗失敗<br />\n<br />\n係咪氣溫會有影響?"},{"pid":"971eadbcded0daab422cd6265b5ddc381e17ee11","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/163503_32c732ac8de654b09b41914a66065b62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F163503_32c732ac8de654b09b41914a66065b62.jpg&h=ac80d769&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"174f038a7ba46ac57d2649615ee7b45b263a21aa","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/163653_76e69f873629482cd64a0fc01b59aa7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F163653_76e69f873629482cd64a0fc01b59aa7b.jpg&h=a76b317c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多罐汽水 只得一罐得 但入面既糖分理應係一樣<br />\n但係點解會出現咁既情況"},{"pid":"bdf2007f215bbc1fe2e9f5b028748d101b65c73a","tid":467131,"uid":14826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"試下chok下罐氣水先浸"},{"pid":"d8af20fe4ed563a224b09ede29c5b4ddb3e396a3","tid":467131,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"可能罐底有氣？<br />\n或者罐內太多空氣"},{"pid":"890e9fa996b2726aaf9c3cb96459c60983c142bc","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"我排上有十罐 新買<br />\n但我剛剛提過可以潛既一罐都浮返<br />\n到底點解？？？"},{"pid":"2dde1c654928bc7187c2ab63f9c7b366b8712ba2","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"關唔關溫度事 ？"},{"pid":"ac741aa44d44b6cfa0fb7fd957692d882167700a","tid":467131,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:08:33.000Z","msg":"入面裝唔滿有氣<br />\n當然個罐都有重量影響到"},{"pid":"5c8dbb4c1e86f39bcea38bbefd32c03f3738fad5","tid":467131,"uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面裝唔滿有氣<br />\n當然個罐都有重量影響到</blockquote><br />\n同意 人地張圖係裝滿晒"},{"pid":"7e6087ac439e3ab5dc3649ee9074c609ee670852","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"其實係我琴日試都無出現呢個問題<br />\n係今日試就好奇怪地發生左呢連串既問題<br />\n<br />\n本身以為係汽水搖得太多入咗氧氣<br />\n但前後十罐汽水 有靜止 搖過 勁搖過 最後都係失敗左<br />\n<br />\n轉左水缸既水 都係失敗<br />\n<br />\n轉左器皿 都係失敗<br />\n<br />\n所以就係到諗關唔關溫度事"},{"pid":"8af72da20655f727d5ab2b89d8a041cd83fb2b50","tid":467131,"uid":91549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"聽日再試多次 睇下用返曬同一物料 睇下有冇唔同 感謝各位"},{"pid":"b33e112c406e53dea54f532a5cd1abfa43e53cca","tid":467131,"uid":14826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"可樂有二氧化碳溶係水入面or谷住係罐入面，應該係咁影響比重。<br />\n要做用低糖檸檬茶同正常做啦。"}]}